---
import GlobalFooter from '../components/GlobalFooter.astro';
export const prerender = true;
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <title>AI CMO Advisor Pricing | Treetop Growth Strategy</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Start at $99 for an AI CMO Starter Report with live competitive data and a 90-day roadmap, upgrade to Monthly at $599/mo for ongoing intelligence, or go fractional for hands-on GTM leadership." />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://treetopgrowthstrategy.com/pricing" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://treetopgrowthstrategy.com/pricing" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="AI CMO Advisor Pricing | Treetop" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="$99 to start, $599/mo for ongoing intelligence, or a fractional CMO to run it with you." />
  <meta property="og:image" content="https://treetopgrowthstrategy.com/og-default.png" />
  <meta property="og:site_name" content="Treetop Growth Strategy" />
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="AI CMO Advisor Pricing | Treetop" />
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="$99 to start, $599/mo ongoing, or go fractional. Live Ahrefs data on every report." />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { background: #050D05; color: #F0FFF0; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-weight: 300; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
    nav { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 50; background: rgba(5,13,5,0.95); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border-bottom: 1px solid #1A3A1A; }
    .nav-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2.5rem; height: 64px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
    .nav-logo { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: 1.3rem; font-style: italic; color: #F0FFF0; text-decoration: none; }
    .nav-link { font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(240,255,240,0.5); text-decoration: none; }
    .nav-link:hover { color: #F0FFF0; }
    .btn-p { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; background: #00C853; color: #050D05; padding: 0.875rem 1.75rem; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; }
    .btn-p:hover { opacity: 0.88; }
    .btn-g { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; background: transparent; color: #F0FFF0; padding: 0.875rem 1.75rem; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; border: 1px solid #1A3A1A; }
    .hero { min-height: 40vh; display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 7rem 2.5rem 4rem; }
    .hero-inner { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%; }
    .lbl { font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #00C853; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; display: block; }
    .hero-h { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.8rem); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.08; color: #F0FFF0; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .hero-h em { color: #00C853; font-style: italic; }
    .hero-sub { font-size: 1rem; color: #8FAF8F; line-height: 1.75; max-width: 620px; }
    section { padding: 5rem 2.5rem; border-top: 1px solid #1A3A1A; }
    .sec-inner { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .price-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
    @media(max-width: 1000px) { .price-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    @media(max-width: 760px) { section { padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem; } .hero { padding: 7rem 1.5rem 3rem; } .hide-mob { display: none !important; } }
    .card { background: #0A1A0A; border: 1px solid #1A3A1A; padding: 2.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
    .card.highlight { border-color: rgba(0,200,83,0.4); position: relative; }
    .card-badge { position: absolute; top: -1px; right: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.62rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; background: #00C853; color: #050D05; padding: 4px 10px; }
    .card-cat { font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #00C853; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .card-name { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: 1.6rem; color: #F0FFF0; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .card-price { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: 3rem; color: #F0FFF0; font-weight: 400; margin: 0.75rem 0 0.25rem; line-height: 1; }
    .card-price em { color: #00C853; font-style: normal; }
    .card-price-meta { font-size: 0.82rem; color: #4A6A4A; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .card-desc { font-size: 0.92rem; color: #8FAF8F; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1.75rem; flex: 1; }
    .card ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .card ul li { font-size: 0.88rem; color: #C0D8C0; padding: 0.45rem 0; padding-left: 1.5rem; position: relative; line-height: 1.55; border-bottom: 1px solid #1A3A1A; }
    .card ul li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .card ul li::before { content: "→"; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #00C853; }
    .card ul li strong { color: #F0FFF0; font-weight: 500; }
    .h2 { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem); font-weight: 400; color: #F0FFF0; margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.15; }
    .body { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #8FAF8F; line-height: 1.75; max-width: 720px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .faq { background: #0A1A0A; border: 1px solid #1A3A1A; padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .faq h3 { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #F0FFF0; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .faq p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: #8FAF8F; line-height: 1.7; }
    .faq a { color: #00C853; text-decoration: none; }
    .cta-box { background: #0A1A0A; border: 1px solid rgba(0,200,83,0.2); padding: 3rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 2rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .cta-text { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: 1.6rem; color: #F0FFF0; }
    .cta-sub { font-size: 0.88rem; color: #8FAF8F; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="/" class="nav-logo">Treetop</a>
    <div class="hide-mob" style="display:flex;gap:2rem;align-items:center;">
      <a href="/ai-cmo-advisor" class="nav-link">AI CMO Advisor</a>
      <a href="/resources" class="nav-link">Resources</a>
      <a href="/about" class="nav-link">About</a>
    </div>
    <a href="/ai-cmo-advisor" class="btn-p" style="padding:0.6rem 1.25rem;font-size:0.78rem;">Get your report &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <span class="lbl">Pricing</span>
    <h1 class="hero-h">Start at $99. <em>Go as deep as you need.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">A $99 starter report built from live competitive data, a monthly subscription that keeps your positioning current, or a fractional CMO actually running it with you. No discovery call required to start.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<section>
  <div class="sec-inner">
    <div class="price-grid">

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-cat">One-time</div>
        <div class="card-name">AI CMO Starter Report</div>
        <div class="card-price"><em>$99</em></div>
        <div class="card-price-meta">one-time, no subscription</div>
        <div class="card-desc">Live Ahrefs data on your domain and up to 3 competitors. A keyword gap analysis. A 90-day roadmap. What I would do first. In your inbox same day.</div>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Competitive snapshot:</strong> DR, traffic, keyword footprint for each competitor</li>
          <li><strong>Keyword gap analysis:</strong> 5-8 high-intent keywords you should be winning</li>
          <li><strong>Content positioning:</strong> angle, voice, and what to stop doing</li>
          <li><strong>Top 3 growth levers:</strong> ranked by ROI for your stage and budget</li>
          <li><strong>90-day roadmap:</strong> concrete milestones by month</li>
          <li><strong>What I'd do first:</strong> the one thing to do this week</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/ai-cmo-advisor" class="btn-p" style="text-align:center;justify-content:center;">Get the report &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <div class="card highlight">
        <div class="card-badge">Most popular</div>
        <div class="card-cat">Monthly</div>
        <div class="card-name">AI CMO Monthly</div>
        <div class="card-price"><em>$599</em></div>
        <div class="card-price-meta">per month, cancel any time</div>
        <div class="card-desc">Your competitive landscape doesn't pause. Monthly keeps you current: updated data, answered questions, and a quarterly strategy reset.</div>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Monthly competitive refresh:</strong> updated Ahrefs data on your domain and up to 3 competitors</li>
          <li><strong>What-changed memo:</strong> what moved and what it means for your plan</li>
          <li><strong>Priority question:</strong> one strategic question answered by Bill within 48 hours</li>
          <li><strong>Quarterly full refresh:</strong> updated report and revised 90-day roadmap every 3 months</li>
          <li><strong>Direct email access:</strong> reply to any report directly</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/ai-cmo-advisor/upgrade" class="btn-p" style="text-align:center;justify-content:center;">Start Monthly &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-cat">Custom</div>
        <div class="card-name">Fractional CMO</div>
        <div class="card-price"><em>Custom</em></div>
        <div class="card-price-meta">quoted as a flat monthly fee</div>
        <div class="card-desc">For when you want someone actually in the seat, not just advising. Hands-on GTM leadership, scoped to your business and stage.</div>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Dynamic ICP system:</strong> refined from your win/loss data and intent signals</li>
          <li><strong>AI-augmented outbound:</strong> built and run, not just recommended</li>
          <li><strong>Pipeline intelligence:</strong> dashboards tying activity to revenue outcomes</li>
          <li><strong>Hands-on execution:</strong> Bill inside your revenue system, not on the sideline</li>
          <li><strong>Flat monthly fee:</strong> never hourly billing</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/fractional-cmo" class="btn-g" style="text-align:center;justify-content:center;">Talk about fractional &rarr;</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="sec-inner">
    <span class="lbl">FAQ</span>
    <h2 class="h2">Common questions</h2>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3>What's the difference between the Starter Report and Monthly?</h3>
      <p>The Starter Report is a one-time snapshot: live Ahrefs data pulled the day you order, a 90-day roadmap, and what to do first. Monthly keeps that data current: competitive positions shift every 30 days, and your Monthly subscription refreshes the analysis, answers your top strategic question each month, and resets the roadmap quarterly.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3>Can I start with the $99 report and upgrade to Monthly?</h3>
      <p>Yes. Most people do. Your Starter Report email includes an upgrade link. Monthly's first refresh shows you exactly what changed since the report.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3>What data does the report actually use?</h3>
      <p>Live Ahrefs API data pulled at the time of your order: domain rating, organic keyword count, estimated monthly traffic, and the top 10 traffic-driving keywords for each domain. Plus the 7 onboarding answers you provide about your business, revenue, competitors, channels, goals, and budget.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3>How fast does the report arrive?</h3>
      <p>Most arrive the same day, typically within a few hours of payment. We build in a short window before delivery so it doesn't feel instant.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3>How do I cancel Monthly?</h3>
      <p>From your Stripe customer portal. No calls, no cancellation fees, no notice period required. Cancel any time and your access runs through the end of the billing period.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3>What if I have a question after my report arrives?</h3>
      <p>Reply to the report email directly. Bill reads it. If you have ongoing questions, Monthly is the right fit: it includes a priority question answered within 48 hours each month plus direct email access.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3>What if I want more than a report or Monthly, someone actually running it?</h3>
      <p>That's the Fractional CMO tier. It's custom-quoted based on scope and stays a flat monthly fee, never hourly. Most fractional clients start with the $99 report or a stretch of Monthly first, so both sides know the fit is right before scoping anything bigger.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="sec-inner">
    <div class="cta-box">
      <div>
        <div class="cta-text">Start with the $99 report.</div>
        <div class="cta-sub">Complete your 7-question intake, pay $99, get your competitive analysis and 90-day roadmap same day. Upgrade only if it's working.</div>
      </div>
      <a href="/ai-cmo-advisor" class="btn-p">Get the report &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<GlobalFooter />

</body>
</html>
